Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.97,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(366,360)}Confessions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second Kira has sent Sakura TV another message for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time they've sent a video and a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I'd better let you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that idiot's gone and done something stupid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't they just sit still and wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying to show the diary on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is it.
