Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:35.72,Diary,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz0.6\move(91,274,91,20,29,4492)}4th: Went to see "Morning Musume" with my friend at the Saitama Super Arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:35.72,Diary,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz0.6\move(92,333,92,77,29,4492)}5th: Last day of the holiday, but I just lazed around at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:35.72,Diary,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz0.6\move(92,416,92,160,0,4492)}7th: School started, but I'd divided the notebooks for different classes \N{\alpha&HFF&}____{\alpha&H00&}with my friends, so I didn't attend.
