Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.77,0:00:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}2006? {\alpha&HFF&}Last year's diary, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.83,0:00:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}2006? Last year's diary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the entry under the 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:43.14,Diary,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\q2\fs32\fry358\frx18\frz4.14\move(63,139,-580,160,0,3630)}28th: Apparently they are going to release the PZ3, which will be more amazing than the PZ2. One to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:43.14,Diary,,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2\frz6.537\fs32\frx18\fry358\move(87,363,-300,363,0,3630)}30th: Confirmed that there was a Shinigami present at the Giant's match in the Tokyo Dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmed that there was a Shinigami present in the Tokyo Dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine that they're suggesting that we do this on the 30th of May.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes out on TV, even the public will realize their intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, {\alpha&HFF&}the only way you can see a Shinigami is if you touch their Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, the only way you can see a Shinigami is if you touch their Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do they--?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.75,Diary,,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2\fs38\move(130,341,-340,341,0,3010)}22nd: {\alpha&HFF&}____{\alpha&H00&}Met up with a friend in Aoyama. Looked at each other's notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I have the eyes of a Shinigami, I'm unable to see my own lifespan. {\alpha&HFF&}Can you explain why that is again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I have the eyes of a Shinigami, I'm unable to see my own lifespan. Can you explain why that is again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:13.30,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.02,0:01:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans possessing a Death Note need only see the lifespans of the humans they are going to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami are unable to see each other's lifespans, and the same principle applies to humans who have Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,22nd of May... {\alpha&HFF&}at Aoyama, we looked at each other's notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,22nd of May... at Aoyama, we looked at each other's notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by "notebooks", they mean "Death Notes", then... {\alpha&HFF&}that's something that only I, as Kira, would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by "notebooks", they mean "Death Notes", then... that's something that only I, as Kira, would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police should be focusing on the entry for the 30th of May...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Confirmed that there was a Shinigami present at the Giant's match in the Tokyo Dome".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably correct in assuming that the entry regarding Aoyama is the real message.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you make of it, Light-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better be careful not to say anything careless here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best that I let him go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, {\alpha&HFF&}it just looks pretty stupid to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it just looks pretty stupid to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! {\alpha&HFF&}It's obvious that they're attempting to meet up with Kira at the Giants's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's obvious that they're attempting to meet up with Kira at the Giants's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Broadcasting this will cause a panic, and the game will be cancelled... don't they even realize this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm honest... this is so dumb, I'm not quite sure how to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we broadcast this diary, {\alpha&HFF&}we'd also have to make the announcement that the match on the 30th will be cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we broadcast this diary, we'd also have to make the announcement that the match on the 30th will be cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, if we don't broadcast the diary, the second Kira won't make their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if we cancel the game, they may get angry, and who knows what they'll do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. {\alpha&HFF&}The second Kira appears to worship Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. The second Kira appears to worship Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be fine in believing their promise to our fake Kira that they won't take innocent lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, first of all, we need to broadcast this diary and announce that the game is cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll announce that on the 30th, {\alpha&HFF&}all the roads surrounding the Tokyo Dome will be controlled by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll announce that on the 30th, all the roads surrounding the Tokyo Dome will be controlled by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lastly, {\alpha&HFF&}we'll send a reply from our fake Kira, agreeing to the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lastly, we'll send a reply from our fake Kira, agreeing to the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... {\alpha&HFF&}you think that they'll show up, despite how tightly the security around that area will be monitored?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you think that they'll show up, despite how tightly the security around that area will be monitored?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that the real Kira will show, {\alpha&HFF&}but I don't know about the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that the real Kira will show, but I don't know about the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know how stupid they really are... {\alpha&HFF&}or even if they truly are as stupid as they seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know how stupid they really are... or {\alpha&HFF&}even if they truly are as stupid as they seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know how stupid they really are... or even if they truly are as stupid as they seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try and see if I can figure out any other hidden messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're using a code that only those with a Shinigami's power would understand, then I won't be able to break it.
Comment: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:49.94,Diary,,0000,0000,0000,,DIARY TRANSLATIONS PLX
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... {\alpha&HFF&}we'll need to ensure that we keep a close surveillance on all of the locations that are mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... we'll need to ensure that we keep a close surveillance on all of the locations that are mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 22nd; met up with a friend in Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 24th; met up with a friend in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realistically, we can't expect any results, but we'll need to pay attention to anyone that's in Aoyama with a notebook, and anyone shopping clothes in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the second Kira is caught, then I have to ensure that I get their notebook at the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in the worst case scenario, kill them and anyone else that's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrange to increase the number of surveillance cameras around Shibuya and Aoyama as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, on the respective days, we'll need to have as many plainclothes policemen as possible at each location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll go, since I'll easily be able to blend in with the crowd at Aoyama and Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I occasionally go to Aoyama and Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm the least likely to look out of place wandering around there with Matsui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, the only person the second Kira is interested in, is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Matsui-san, let's leave the plans for Aoyama and Shibuya until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got that. Light-kun, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I get back outside and switch my phone back on, this always happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to observe Light-kun carefully during those two days as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is confidential, so please keep this to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"As long as my suspicions aren't at 0%, be suspicious of his every move"... is that what he's saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! You're home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me to keep my assistance with the investigation a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a girlfriend at the university now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}Onii-chan's got a girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Onii-chan's got a girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm an 18 year old university student; it's only natural, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, I'm an 18 year old university student; it's only natural, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu, you've got to try harder too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! {\alpha&HFF&}I-I don't want to try hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! I-I don't want to try hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light? {\alpha&HFF&}What about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light? What about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had room service at the hotel, so I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan! What do you mean by "hotel"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What kind of scandal have I unearthed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ryuk... {\alpha&HFF&}there's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ryuk... there's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're able to answer, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Shinigami on Earth allowed to talk to one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that from the moment I possessed a human, it became against the rules for me to do that kind of thing without the human's permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there isn't really a law against talking, so the other Shinigami may come and talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you mean that there's a possibility that when the second Kira's Shinigami sees you, they'd be allowed to tell them that I am Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, they wouldn't. It depends on their personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}is is safe for me to assume that your personality is what I believe it to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is is safe for me to assume that your personality is what I believe it to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. {\alpha&HFF&}If I saw a human with a Shinigami, I wouldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. If I saw a human with a Shinigami, I wouldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}I think that's the right choice, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think that's the right choice, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}The fake Kira's already thought it through this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The fake Kira's already thought it through this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama is a huge place. {\alpha&HFF&}I was doing some research on how to go about looking for them, and I found this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama is a huge place. I was doing some research on how to go about looking for them, and I found this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 22nd, there's an event at the "Note Blue" nightclub.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.66,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama literally translates to "Blue Mountain"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blue"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and "Note"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that they've put a bit of effort into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that they're smarter than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although if that's true, I may have to be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it seems that going to this "Note Blue" might be worth a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't want them to find out that you're Kira, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... Light-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my friends at the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my cousin, Tarou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his first time in Tokyo, and he says he wants to have fun somewhere like Aoyama or Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's do our best for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also looking for a girlfriend, any applicants?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I expected from Light-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would think that there are police present in this group of young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I move around in a group, {\alpha&HFF&}even if Ryuk gets seen, they won't know who he's possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I move around in a group, even if Ryuk gets seen, {\alpha&HFF&}they won't know who he's possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I move around in a group, even if Ryuk gets seen, they won't know who he's possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, it'll act as a wall against L's surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad for investigative purposes either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remains is to watch the entrance of "Note Blue" prior to, and after the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami... {\alpha&HFF&}Tsuki-kun, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami... Tsuki-kun, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:24.54,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,月 = "Tsuki" (moon). Read as Light in this case, but this is not shown by the written form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only person whose lifespan I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it! He's Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that it'd be this easy to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rem, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, already? After all the effort you've put into meeting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be bad for me to go up to him with all these people around and say something like, "I'm so happy to meet you, Kira-san!", wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know his name, it'll be easy to find out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an unusual name, after all.
Comment: 0,0:09:54.99,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oooh! {\alpha&HFF&}So it's written "Tsuki" but pronounced as "Light"!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.82,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oooh! So it's written "Tsuki" but pronounced as "Light"!
