Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.54,LongNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6F6862&\3c&HC5C2BE&\frz18.488\frx352\fry6\pos(364,335)}Height:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.54,LongNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6F6862&\3c&HC5C2BE&\frz18.488\frx352\fry6\pos(354,287)}D.O.B.: {\alpha&HFF&}_____{\alpha&H00&}February 28th, 1989
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, he's pretty amazing, isn't he, this Yagami Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, while he was in his second and third year at Junior High, he was the National Tennis Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, for Toudai University's Entrance Ceremony this year, he gave the speech as the freshers' representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no photo, but it can't be anyone else with a name like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never guessed that Kira would be so young and handsome...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is far better than I'd imagined it would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are places unashamedly selling registers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is such a twisted place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know his address too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, on both the 22nd in Aoyama and the 24th in Shibuya, there was no evidence of any suspicious activity occurring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remains now is the Dome on the 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no one suspicious at "Note Blue" either...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that it's really going to happen at the Dome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! Sakura TV have received another message from the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's postmarked the 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:19.68,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to find Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:24.16,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,To everyone at the TV station and the police force, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}Impossible?! Where? At Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible?! {\alpha&HFF&}Where? At Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible?! Where? {\alpha&HFF&}At Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible?! Where? At Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did their Shinigami see Ryuk and tell them that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}In the crowd, it should have been impossible to tell who Ryuk was possessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... In the crowd, it should have been impossible to tell who Ryuk was possessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took every precaution to ensure that I wasn't followed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this really is connected to the diary... {\alpha&HFF&}and was really posted on the 23rd... the only date it leaves is the 22nd, in Aoyama, as a corresponding date.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this really is connected to the diary... and was really posted on the 23rd... {\alpha&HFF&}the only date it leaves is the 22nd, in Aoyama, as a corresponding date.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this really is connected to the diary... and was really posted on the 23rd... the only date it leaves is the 22nd, in Aoyama, as a corresponding date.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only people to have gone from headquarters were Matsuda and Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is Yagami Light Kira, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet there's absolutely no proof that it happened in Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, they've found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that Kira and the second Kira have joined forces...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we don't know for sure that they've joined forces yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second Kira only said that they'd "found" Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may yet have to make contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've progressed this far, {\alpha&HFF&}the only thing that we can do is have the police appeal to the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've progressed this far, the only thing that we can do is have the police appeal to the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appeal to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}The police will need to offer the second Kira a favorable deal if they tell us who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The police will need to offer the second Kira a favorable deal if they tell us who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things can't get any worse for you, can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good... {\alpha&HFF&}I have absolutely no idea how this second Kira may react...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good... I have absolutely no idea how this second Kira may react...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, there's no way that I can stop them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:53.54,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira doesn't already know who you are, it's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:57.33,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't approach Kira purely for the fun of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:01.47,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If you come in contact with Kira, you will almost certainly die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:03.05,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only be used!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:08.35,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,All you should do now, is to think carefully about the value of human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.56,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us all the information you have on Kira, and atone for your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.78,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Save the people of the world from the fear of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so this is the choice you've made...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. {\alpha&HFF&}My name is Amane Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. My name is Amane Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to return an important notebook that Light-san left behind at university.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-{\alpha&HFF&}Please wait for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notebook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm Amane Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you. I'm Amane Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching the TV, and I thought that you might worry about me, so I just had to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Note?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fake Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you sure that it's okay? {\alpha&HFF&}I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you sure that it's okay? I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, {\alpha&HFF&}she's gone through all the effort of bringing this over, so could we get some tea or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, she's gone through all the effort of bringing this over, so could we get some tea or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you about this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you really haven't traded your eyes, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you trade your eyes with a Shinigami, {\alpha&HFF&}you're able to see people's names and lifespans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you trade your eyes with a Shinigami, you're able to see people's names and lifespans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but{\alpha&HFF&} you're unable to see the lifespan of someone who has a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're unable to see the lifespan of someone who has a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\alpha&HFF&}I-I didn't know that much about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I-I didn't know that much about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I've understood that much, {\alpha&HFF&}but if you'd been caught, Kira's secrets would've been revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I've understood that much, but if you'd been caught, Kira's secrets would've been revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. {\alpha&HFF&}So far, I haven't been caught, and if I do as you say from now on, I won't get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. So far, I haven't been caught, and if I do as you say from now on, I won't get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll see L's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me your girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I handle this the wrong way, I could end up dead, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day in Aoyama, there were triple the usual number of surveillance cameras operating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you went to Aoyama that day, you would have been captured on tape somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to become close after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even meeting each other now is risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least try to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are photos of me on the day I went to Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that she's unrecognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about fingerprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All those things you sent to the TV station were covered in the same fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those aren't my fingerprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I think through things a little before I act!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until recently, I was living in Kansai, and I had a friend there who was interested in the occult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a fake video containing footage of spirits and approached her about sending it to some TV stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was really into the idea, and I got her to dub ten copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I copied the "Kira" over to them, without getting my own prints on them, and added the audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your friend doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you told me to kill them, I'd do it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still refuse to trust me, {\alpha&HFF&}you can look after this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still refuse to trust me, you can look after this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you only look after it, I'll still be the owner, so I should still be able to use the power of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, I won't be able to kill you, but if I become useless to you, you can kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she willing to go this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you could already have torn out a page of the Death Note and hidden it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to be so suspicious of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if I really am just used by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she say such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A year ago, my parents were murdered right in front of me by a burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive that... {\alpha&HFF&}yet the trial dragged on and on. Eventually they judged that he'd been falsely accused..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive that... yet the trial dragged on and on. Eventually they judged that he'd been falsely accused..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then... Kira passed judgment on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, Kira is an absolute being!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter... {\alpha&HFF&}no matter what, I wanted to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter... no matter what, I wanted to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went through all this trouble for the sole purpose of meeting Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was able to implement the bare minimum of countermeasures against surveillance cameras and leaving fingerprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not as stupid as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, {\alpha&HFF&}she's saying that she'll do as I say from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, she's saying that she'll do as I say from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be your boyfriend, but I can pretend to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes of yours, which you traded half your remaining life for in order to find and aid me, will be a great weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll try my hardest to make you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'll try my hardest to make you love me.
